node.description: Two central roads have been closed.
node.content: ["A vehicle has collided with pedestrians on a main Taup\u014d road.\u00a0", "According to police, emergency services were called at 1:42pm to a collision between a vehicle and pedestrians on Lake Terrace.", "Motorists are being asked to stay clear of the area as both Lake Terrace and Pataka Rd have been closed.", "More information is expected later on Thursday."]
